{vay}

EFACEpRay

Erethay isay uchmay uthtray inay ethay olday ayingsay aboutay ethay ifficultyday ofay eeingsay
ethay oodway orfay ethay eestray.  Itay isay ethay aimay ofay isthay ortshay ookbay otay eepkay ethay
umbernay ofay ethay eestray asay ewfay asay ossiblepay osay atthay ethay oodway, asay aay olewhay,
aymay ebay earlyclay isiblevay.

Itay isay esignedday otay ovidepray olarsschay anday eirthay eacherstay ithway anay outlineay
ofay ethay ostmay importantay actsfay inay ethay istoryhay ofay ankindmay upay otay ethay ateday
ofay ethay irmfay establishmentay ofay ethay Omanray Empireay anday ethay inalfay
estructionday ofay Erusalemjay--aay ateday atay ichwhay ethay ariousvay eadsthray ofay ethay
orystay omecay ogethertay otay aay ointpay.  Inay orderay otay avoiday onfusingcay ethay
earnerlay, anday otay enableay imhay otay etgay aay earclay iewvay ofay ethay ostmay importantay
actsfay, allay esslay importantay actsfay anday amesnay anday atesday avehay eenbay omitteday.

Ithway uchsay anay outlineay inay ishay indmay, ethay olarschay, omingcay otay ethay udystay ofay
aay articularpay ationnay oray eriodpay, ouldshay ebay ableay otay itfay atthay ationnay oray
eriodpay intoay itsay operpray aceplay.  Inay ethay absenceay ofay anyay uchsay outlineay, ehay
ustmay ecessarilynay ebay atay aay osslay otay owknay ethay earingbay ofay isthay oray atthay
episodeay onay ethay olewhay eatgray orystay.

{ivay}

Iay avehay otay ecordray, eryvay atefullygray, ymay eepday obligationay otay Mray. Ray. Bay.
Attimerlay orfay eadingray isthay ookbay inay MSay., anday orfay anymay aluablevay
uggestionssay anday emendationsay.

Hay. Gay. Hay.




