  Ixay. Acedonmay
  IIxay. Omeray anday Arthagecay
  IIIxay. Omeray atay Omehay anday inay ethay Eastay
  IVxay. Omeray Istressmay ofay ethay Orldway
  XVay. Oublestray inay ethay Eastay
  IxVay. Ethay Ispersalday ofay ethay Ewsjay
  IIxVay. Owhay ethay Eadsthray awdray ogethertay
  Indexay




